## Objective

This tutorial is little how to on nginx + lua with some basic and yet praticle examples which can be handy as in when require.

# Quick start

1. Download and install openresty 

$ wget https://openresty.org/download/openresty-1.11.2.2.tar.gz

$ tar -xzvf openresty-1.11.2.2.tar.gz

$ cd openresty-1.11.2.2


# Note : The package comes bundled with almost all the core and 3rd party modules you need however I had download one addional module "nginx-auth-request-module"
# More on it in "blog-page-counter-using-openresty-lua"

 

